summary: Experienced in both startups and large commercial businesses, I am a results-driven young professional in international trade, logistics, and new business development. I excel at managing supply chain logistics, ensuring compliance, identifying growth opportunities, and driving revenue through effective market research and strategic planning. With expertise in coffee trading, I navigate complexities of the global coffee market and bring high-quality coffee to consumers worldwide. Let's work collaboratively to achieve meaningful results.
